reviews_data.review_text:
Came here the other day to grab some matcha after a long night. This spot caught my friends eye, so we finally decided to check it out.

First impression—it’s super clean, aesthetically pleasing, and has a good amount of space whether you want to sit inside or chill outside. It’s a cute place to catch up with work on a laptop or catch up with friends.

We were greeted right away, and the vibe was really welcoming. I ordered a tea and the strawberry matcha that’s been trending lately. I had to tweak it a bit—oat milk instead of regular and no cold foam since I’m lactose intolerant. The cashier was super patient, especially since I was ordering tea for a friend and we were a little all over the place with flavors. Shoutout to both the cashier and barista! They were both really kind and helpful.

Now, the matcha was just okay for me. Not bad, but not something I’d rush back for. That said, my friends really liked their drinks, so I think I just didn’t pick the right thing.

I’d come back to try one of their coffee options and hopefully sit around. The space is inviting and I saw outlets, which is always a plus.
Excellent and polite staff and a fun clean/environment. Huge selection of great breakfast and lunch food. Very convenient location, and dog friendly, free pup cups!
Good coffee and service, lots of drink options

reviews_data.author_title: Keep It A Secret Entertainment, LLC
reviews_data.review_text: Great time, good coffee, with excellent giveaways for the grand opening today!
Nice baristas, nice facility, but my goodness that coffee is not very good. :(

Great people great atmosphere.  I live in the northeast and found these by word of mouth and all I can say is wow!  They are super inviting and the staff is second to non.  I highly recommend the coffee republic brand and have been to almost all  the locations
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Thank you so much, Michael! We're thrilled to hear that you enjoyed the welcoming atmosphere and our amazing team at Coffee Republic. It’s fantastic that word of mouth led you to us all the way from the Northeast—what a compliment! We truly appreciate your support and your kind words about our brand. 

Next time you're in Trade Street, we’d love to see you again at our coffee shop for another Iced Latte (or maybe something new to try!). See you soon! Cheers!

reviews_data.review_text: Love this place! Great vibe and awesome coffee and drink selection. Really close to uptown too so easy to get to.
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Thank you, Laura! We're so glad you love the vibe and our coffee selection. Being close to uptown makes it even easier to stop by for your favorite drink! 

Next time you're in the area, why not visit Coffee Republic on Trade Street for another great coffee experience? See you again soon! Cheers!

reviews_data.review_text: Great coffee! Great atmosphere!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you for your kind words, Louise! We're delighted to hear you enjoyed the coffee and atmosphere. If you're ever in Trade Street, visit Coffee Republic for another fantastic coffee experience! We look forward to welcoming you again soon. Cheers!

reviews_data.review_text:
Ordered an iced vanilla latte and it was probably the worst iced coffee I have had in Charlotte. I’m not sure if the espresso sat too long or how they even make drinks (it looks like some sort of machine that mixes the syrup with the milk, almost like a gas station?) but I will not go back. I threw out the coffee and went to Starbucks. I tried to support something new but yeah, it’s a no go for me. Coco, Starbucks, Water Bean, etc… all nearby and so much better.

On the plus side, the energy ball is good.
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Hi Anthony,

We’re sorry to hear that your iced vanilla latte didn’t meet your expectations. We strive to serve quality coffee, and your feedback is valuable in helping us improve. Our drinks are crafted with fresh espresso, and we’ll certainly review our process to ensure consistency.

We’re glad you enjoyed the energy ball! If you’re ever open to giving us another try, we’d love to make it right. Feel free to reach out to us at daniel@coffeerepub.com so we can learn more about your experience.

Next time you’re in the Trade Street area, we invite you to visit Coffee Republic. We hope to see you again!


Warm regards,
Daniel Coco
Charlotte Area Market Manager
Coffee Republic

reviews_data.review_text: I loved the Barista who helped us out. The inside is cute and a perfect place to work, but I would not order the Matcha here if you love Matcha.
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Hi Mireya,

Thank you for your kind words about our barista and the cozy atmosphere! We’re so glad you enjoyed the space. We appreciate your feedback on the Matcha and will take it into consideration. 

We hope to see you again soon at Coffee Republic on Trade Street. See you!

Thank you so much, Molly! We love hearing that you enjoy our coffee, atmosphere, and friendly baristas. The Sugar Daddy is definitely a fan favorite—we’re glad you love it!

We’d love to see you again at Coffee Republic on Trade Street for more good vibes and great coffee! See you!

We look forward to seeing you again soon at Coffee Republic Trade Street!

Next time you’re in the area, be sure to stop by Coffee Republic on Trade Street for another great coffee experience. Looking forward to serving you again soon! Cheers!
